Package Food

Class Food

  • java.lang.Object
    • Food.Food

  • public class Food
extends java.lang.Object
    The Food class is an ADT that represents a food item by its id, descriptor, and nutritional values. It accepts 3 arguments; the id (int), the descriptor (String of tags separated by commas), and the nutritional values ( Note that the inputed descriptor is converted to an array of its tags
